RIGHT       | F1_2  | F2_2  | F3_2  | F4_2  | TH1_2 | TH2_2 |                 | TH2_2 | TH1_2 | F4_2  | F3_2  | F2_2  | F1_2  |
DOWN        | F1_3  | F2_3  | F3_3  | F4_3  | TH1_3 | TH2_3 |                 | TH2_3 | TH1_3 | F4_3  | F3_3  | F2_3  | F1_4  |
LEFT        | F1_4  | F2_4  | F3_4  | F4_4  | TH1_4 | TH2_4 |                 | TH2_4 | TH1_4 | F4_4  | F3_4  | F2_4  | F1_5  |
CLICK       | F1_5  | F2_5  | F3_5  | F4_5  | TH1_5 | TH2_5 |                 | TH2_5 | TH1_5 | F4_5  | F3_5  | F2_5  | F1_5  |
